* TI template for DCM solvated solute run
* Mike DEVEREUX (2017)
*

BOMLEV 0
PRNLEVEL 2 NODE 0

SET PATH ../common

READ RTF CARD        NAME -
 @PATH/zeroed.top

READ PARAM CARD        NAME -
 @PATH/RRR

OPEN UNIT 10 READ CARD NAME @PATH/TTT
READ SEQUENCE PDB UNIT 10
GENERATE SOLU
REWIND UNIT 10
READ COOR PDB UNIT 10
CLOSE UNIT 10

OPEN UNIT 10 READ CARD NAME @PATH/UUU
READ SEQUENCE PDB UNIT 10
GENERATE WAT NOANgle NODIhedral
REWIND UNIT 10
READ COOR PDB UNIT 10
CLOSE UNIT 10

OPEN UNIT 40 CARD READ NAME @PATH/lambda_0.0.dcm
DCM IUDCM 40 TSHIFT 
CLOSE UNIT 40

PERT SELE SEGI SOLU END
SCALAR CHARGE SET 0. SELE SEGI SOLU END


COOR STAT
CALC BOXX = (?XMAX - ?XMIN -1.0)
CRYSTAL DEFI CUBIC @BOXX @BOXX @BOXX 90. 90. 90. 
CRYSTAL BUILD nope 0
IMAGE BYRES XCEN 0.0 YCEN 0.0 ZCEN 0.0 SELE ALL END
SHAKE BONH TOL 1.0E-8 PARA

NBONDS ATOM - !EWALD PMEWALD KAPPA 0.32 -
CUTNB 14.0 CTOFNB 12.0 CTONnb 10.0 cutim 14.00 -
vatom vdistance -
VSWITCH SHIFT CDIE eps 1.0 e14fac 1.0 wmin 1.5


OPEN UNIT 40 CARD READ NAME @PATH/lambda_1.0.dcm
DCM S1 40 
CLOSE UNIT 40

open read unit 32 card name @PATH/ZZZ
read coor dynr curr unit 32

DYNA LEAP RESTART NSTEP SSS TIMESTEP 0.001 -
LLL
   FIRSTT 298.0  FINALT 298.0  TSTRUC 298.0       -
   IPRFRQ 1000  NTRFRQ 5000                       -
   IHBFRQ 0  INBFRQ -1                            -
   NPRINT 100                                     -
   IASORS 0  ISCVEL 0                             -
   IEQFRQ 0  ICHECW 1  TWINDH 5.0  TWINDL -5.0    -
   CPT PCONst PREF 1.0 PGAMMA 20.0 PMASs 500      -
   TBATH 298.                                     -
   IUNREAD 32  IUNWRITE -1  IUNCRD -1  NSAVCRD 0 

STOP
